    <item>
      <title>拜登退出敲响警钟，特朗普交易充满矛盾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街在预测和交易关键选举方面有着糟糕的记录，即使是在最好的情况下也是如此。现在，随着乔·拜登的退出颠覆了美国总统竞选，根据最新的政治头条进行投资的危险性已凸显出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:47:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股大跌之际，对冲基金积极削减股票风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hedge-funds-aggressively-cut-risks-in-stocks-amid-big-tech-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球最大的科技公司遭受重创，对冲基金上周以 2021 年 1 月模因股热潮以来最快的速度抛售获利股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hedge-funds-aggressively-cut-risks-in-stocks-amid-big-tech-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行将对工党的英国增长计划进行现实检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/boe-set-to-give-labour-a-reality-check-over-uk-growth-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将英国经济增长率提升至 2.5% 的雄心预计将在下周英国央行发布新的预测时受到打击。]]></description>
